    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge your friends to fast-paced, mind-bending arcade action!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll into this fresh take on the falling block puzzle genre with a focus on competition. Take on the High Rollers in Arcade mode or challenge other players in local and online versus modes. With multiple ways to score, the chaining possibilities are endless! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                               <strong>Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/a23022362bed93aa251653e8d8fb6cdb.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/a23022362bed93aa251653e8d8fb6cdb.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> Versus -  Challenge your friends locally in the flagship mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> Online - Make new rivals in the ranked online versus mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/bd0ca1ec7e58711cf9df9fbbbe58d9f6.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/bd0ca1ec7e58711cf9df9fbbbe58d9f6.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> Survival - Go for high scores in a race against the clock </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/85ac5e2ce1297cb3ef63549a356537eb.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/85ac5e2ce1297cb3ef63549a356537eb.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> Arcade - Battle the High Rollers in this classic arcade-style mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/472ce6b8456bc628fb734ba0410922b2.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/472ce6b8456bc628fb734ba0410922b2.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> Mission - Take on over 75 missions and puzzles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                                <strong>Scoring</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/b2a9edae59847183ab6331ff160288d7.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/b2a9edae59847183ab6331ff160288d7.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=16 height=17 /></picture></span>  <strong>Flip</strong>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/b2a9edae59847183ab6331ff160288d7.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/b2a9edae59847183ab6331ff160288d7.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=16 height=17 /></picture></span>                             </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                              Stack matching dice to increment  to the next value <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/bed4dab7e20e40be1dbdddab82f6ea69.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" width=544 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/bed4dab7e20e40be1dbdddab82f6ea69.webm?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/bed4dab7e20e40be1dbdddab82f6ea69.mp4?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/85c6fb90beb33967a326b382c90a1c35.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/85c6fb90beb33967a326b382c90a1c35.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span>  <strong>Sixer</strong>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/85c6fb90beb33967a326b382c90a1c35.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/85c6fb90beb33967a326b382c90a1c35.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                               Create a 6 through flips to clear it  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/dbc9c63589fbbab368cba1c676171b27.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" width=544 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/dbc9c63589fbbab368cba1c676171b27.webm?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/dbc9c63589fbbab368cba1c676171b27.mp4?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> <strong>Rollout</strong>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.apng?t=1767501284\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/90558aee91b46b57dfbf8d468982845d.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=16 /></picture></span>                                    </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                        Line up 3 or more identical dice horizontally <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/e078613d463ad595c2c930c42ca551e1.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" width=544 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/e078613d463ad595c2c930c42ca551e1.webm?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/e078613d463ad595c2c930c42ca551e1.mp4?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>          </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                Chain together these techniques to score big and attack your opponent! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/4c34b5d5192a2fd915c1a864978c3989.poster.avif?t=1767501284\" width=544 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/4c34b5d5192a2fd915c1a864978c3989.webm?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096150/extras/4c34b5d5192a2fd915c1a864978c3989.mp4?t=1767501284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
